                            <comment id="16911123" author="bwahlen" created="Tue, 20 Aug 2019 08:54:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;these errors they did not appear until 8.1.1 &lt;br/&gt;
 after upgrading solr to 8.2.0 still everything is fine.&lt;br/&gt;
